Here's an example of an Nginx configuration file (`nginx_config.conf`):

```
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name your_domain.com;

    location / {
        proxy_pass http://localhost:8000;
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
    }
}
